  <img loading="lazy" src="/sites/default/files/styles/2015_hero/public/2025-02/Header_Explain_it_in_60_seconds_High_Luminosity_LHC.png?itok=kSg6BJE6" width="1600" height="900" alt="Conceptual illustration of a firehose shooting out particles" />





